title: Build Your Own Solar Panels - DYI
description:
This is an extensive collection of do it your self information on building your own solar panels. It shows you how to build from scratch on-grid and off-grid systems.
Buy solar cells, solder them together into solar panels. Then build a solar array and connect it your home.

I paid a lot of money for this CD.
I believe everyone should convert to solar power and put the electric companies out of business.
Who knows what the future brings?
Be prepared with your own solar powered energy system.

This is an ISO file for creating the CD.
